            "summary": "In San Francisco, Elastic (NYSE: ESTC) revealed its financial outcomes for Q4 and the full fiscal year concluding on April 30, 2025. Q4 Fiscal 2025 displayed notable figures: total revenue reached $388 million, marking a 16% rise compared to the prior year, both as reported and in constant currency. Elastic Cloud revenue was notably up by 23% year-over-year, totaling $182 million, as reported and in constant currency. Furthermore, the GAAP operating loss stood at $12 million.",
